org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.client

Interface GetConnectionIdExtendedOperationHandlerCfgClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationClient, ExtendedOperationHandlerCfgClient

    public interface GetConnectionIdExtendedOperationHandlerCfgClient
extends ExtendedOperationHandlerCfgClient
    A client-side interface for reading and modifying Get Connection Id Extended Operation Handler settings.

    The Get Connection Id Extended Operation Handler provides a mechanism for clients to obtain the internal connection ID that the server uses to reference their client connection.
